00:28:15,541 --> 00:28:17,541
[footsteps approaching]

321
00:28:21,375 --> 00:28:22,375
[Kengo] Oh.

322
00:28:23,333 --> 00:28:24,208
Welcome.

323
00:28:30,083 --> 00:28:33,166
Do you know where Saeko's off to?

324
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:35,375
No.

325
00:28:52,375 --> 00:28:53,291
What is it?

326
00:28:54,833 --> 00:28:55,791
