343
00:29:47,875 --> 00:29:50,125
You don't need to
think of yourself like that.

344
00:29:51,416 --> 00:29:52,583
Let me rephrase.

345
00:29:53,375 --> 00:29:55,250
You should stop thinking like that.

346
00:29:58,500 --> 00:30:00,250
Just your being here,

347
00:30:01,791 --> 00:30:05,541
it goes a long way to making folks happy.

348
00:30:05,625 --> 00:30:06,666
Lots of people.

349
00:30:09,041 --> 00:30:09,958
So,

350
00:30:11,416 --> 00:30:14,125
