351
00:30:18,750 --> 00:30:20,291
I really appreciate it.

352
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:23,666
But…

353
00:30:28,250 --> 00:30:30,041
I can't afford to do that now.

354
00:30:35,291 --> 00:30:36,291
[sighs]

355
00:30:38,041 --> 00:30:39,041
